        The trailer racked up more than 10 million views in less than 24 hours. It suggests the new film is following the original story - although with Simba looking so clear in the trailer, some people are worried about what that means for his dad...
    
      
              
              Image Copyright @woIvern
              @woIvern
          
          Report
      
          
                  Image Copyright @woIvern
                  @woIvern
              
              Report
          
    


                
                
                
                
                
            
            
        It's directed by Jon Favreau, who was behind the live-action remake of The Jungle Book.Donald Glover will play Simba, Beyonce will play his love interest Nala and Chiwetel Ejiofor will play his uncle Scar. "It is a director's dream to assemble a talented team like this to bring this classic story to life," Jon said.
    
      
              
              Image Copyright @Disney
              @Disney
          
          Report
      
          
                  Image Copyright @Disney
